Text:
No neeed for key, just install this as a theme, put anything in the API key box and it will activate......

....But use it at your peril!....somethings not quite right about it. It's a nulled version, and can't be updated and the coding inside seems to search for other sites such as GoDaddy and Hostgator once activated. I deleted it as fast as a rat up a drainpipe.
